oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Wil Maring & Robert Bowlin - 2018-11-10
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Wil Maring & Robert Bowlin as part of the Bluegrass and Beyond celebration from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 10, 2018. Recording includes sound check for the next performer. Second performance of four.
